edu.frontrange.csc240.a12

Class ByDoubleField

  • Object
    • edu.frontrange.csc240.a12.ByDoubleField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<AreaData>

    public class ByDoubleField
extends Object
implements java.util.Comparator<AreaData>
    A comparator to order by the given double field of a state or territory. If the double values are equal, then the ordering is done by the natural ordering of the AreaData object.

    Note: this comparator imposes orderings that are inconsistent with equals.

    Version:
    1.2, 2016-08-22, CSC-241, Assignment 5 (see Instructions)
    Author:
    Dr. Bruce K. Haddon, Instructor
